{
  "stem": "15082.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'd stop someplace, and go into a farm, and beg for some food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'd get it, luckily.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sometimes, you got nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And just try to stay out of the main roads, just because there was a lot of forest there that would interconnect between fields and forest.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had a pretty good idea where it-- you'd ask once in a while, how to get to the next village, or the next village, till I worked my way back.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I came back, I came back to Podkamien.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my mom and dad were there, hidden already, they couldn't walk around freely, because at that point already it was almost Judenfrei at the time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through this Marczeniek.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know enough to contact this Polish man.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was still some Jews hidden in the town, because there was a group that kept working it with [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not a labor camp, but just a group of people that they kept them working.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Ukrainian police was watching over them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They'd have to go every day to work, and do this type of work, whether it was cleaning the police stations, or doing road work, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There wasn't too much-- it was a small group that was kept back there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that point, we did not really make up-- or put it better, we were not offered by Mr.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Marczeniek to come and stay there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was frightening, I guess, because they would have killed him if they knew he was harboring Jews, hiding Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the year of-- that was in '43, just before the high holidays.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We all embarked into a forest, a group of Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we figured that we can hide out in the forest.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
